<p data-ke-size="size16"><span style="background-color: #fafafa; color: #009a87;">사용자(User)에게&nbsp;접속권한,&nbsp;오브젝트&nbsp;생성권한,&nbsp;DBA&nbsp;권한&nbsp;등을&nbsp;부여할&nbsp;수&nbsp;있는&nbsp;명령어</span></p>
